<br>
I can't believe i really have it!!  To accomplish an epic is probably one of the most rewarding experiences of any characters carrer.  But my reward was not so much in the leafblower itself, or in any mob that went down to get it. My reward is in my wonderful friends that made it happen for me.  Many of them wear your tag and do EA honor.  <br>
<br>
We took down 6 mobs in two days and i think that goes above and beyond the call of friendship and i am truely humbled by such displays of loyalty and generousity.  My special thanks to all that helped me, but specifically want to name three of my dearest friends who are always there when i need them.  Kklan one of my oldest friends on EQ.  God i remember when you used to make me studded armour!)))  Riphen. . . wow was there ever a more consistant shoulder to lean on.  And eriul . . . well what can i say about the ranga . . .i am so glad we stood beside each other as we both turned in our final pieces for our epics.  We started them together and we ended them together.  Thank you.<br>
<br>
You know this game has such highs and such lows.  Some days i laugh so hard i cry.  Some days i cry so hard i laugh.  Some days you can't wait to log on and other days you just want to quit in frustration.  But there is a scarlet thread that runs through all of that, and that thread holds it all together i think for most of us.  And that is our friends.  <br>
<br>
So thank you all that helped me anywhere along that epic journey.  You will always have my unwavering respect and affection. <br>
<br>
Kajira Firelight  <p>I have a whip, and I am not afraid to use it!  /Crack</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub75.ezboard.com/uvela29.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vela29</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 274<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/28/02 10:49:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/feternaladvocatesvazaelle66917frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=416.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Leafblower and one happy dr00d</span><hr size=1> Congratulations on getting your epic Kajira.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub75.ezboard.com/usoulreeverx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SoulreeverX</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Undertaker</span><br>  Posts: 739<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/28/02 10:52:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub75.ezboard.com/feternaladvocatesvazaelle66917frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=416.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://faceweb-004.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/62/2366562.jpg?flezbwidth=&flezbheight=200?flezbwidth=200&flezbheight=200?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=